Package api.equinix.javasdk.ibxsmartview.enums

package api.equinix.javasdk.ibxsmartview.enums
IBX SmartView enumerations for the Equinix Java SDK. Defines typed constants for level types that categorize hierarchy nodes, alert statuses for monitoring thresholds, channel types for sensor classification, data point types for environmental and power measurements, reading granularity intervals, and other IBX SmartView domain values used throughout the monitoring and alerting system.
